    "body": "This log means the P2P agent started\r\n2022-03-29 08:31:27.174+10:00 | vert.x-eventloop-thread-2 | INFO | PeerDiscoveryAgent | P2P peer discovery agent started and listening on /0:0:0:0:0:0:0:0:30303\r\nAnd then once sufficient useful peers are obtained, full sync starts with something like this\r\n2022-03-29 09:08:26.831+10:00 | nioEventLoopGroup-3-3 | INFO | SyncTargetManager | Found common ancestor with peer Peer 0x0b7150c1adbaec3bc6... at block 0\r\nfast sync is a bit different\r\nonce it has (minimum) 5 peers\r\n2022-03-29 09:22:10.702+10:00 | EthScheduler-Timer-0 | INFO  | FastSyncActions | Selecting block number 5062554 as fast sync pivot block.\r\nThen it waits for 5 confirmations of pivot block which can take a while and obviously depends on quality of peers\r\n2022-03-29 09:37:16.549+10:00 | nioEventLoopGroup-3-5 | INFO  | PivotBlockConfirmer | Confirmed pivot block at 5062554: 0xd4e574268148d0544f7a74402fe80dde2cfc8cf2ca5901f60d373eeb243b18d5\r\nthen can download world state\r\n2022-03-29 09:37:16.558+10:00 | nioEventLoopGroup-3-5 | INFO  | FastWorldStateDownloader | Begin downloading world state from peers for block 5062554 (0xd4e574268148d0544f7a74402fe80dde2cfc8cf2ca5901f60d373eeb243b18d5). State root 0x7ca542145e6c33e8aea6142133d1d195fb02ef38a63ff3450a8011a00ef2c953",
